properties.name: The Devil May Care
properties.description:
Tomorrow is Halloween. This is ride 222 and you multiply that by 3 and you get you know what. There may be other portents and convergences that we are not aware of too But we're not going to do any digging into it. We won't even take a quick look at Wikipedia. No. Because, while the devil may care, we do not.

What we do care about is climbing some hills, and riding off-road, and climbing some off-road hills. Not to mention bridges and tunnels and exploration and views. So there is going to be plenty of all that. We'll let El Diablo worry about all that other stuff.
